description: I'm so tired, I haven't slept a wink. I'm so tired, my mind is on the blink. I wonder should I get up, and fix myself a drink

Keyboard Cat is an Internet meme. It consists of a video from 1984 of a female cat called "Fatso" wearing a blue shirt and "playing" an upbeat rhythm on an electronic keyboard. The video was posted to YouTube under the title "charlie schmidt's cool cats" in June 2007.
